HEADWORD: Guttiferous
<hw>Gut*tif"er*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>Yielding gum or resinous substances.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>Pertaining to a natural order of trees and shrubs
